English:
"User has been forced to log out.
Unable to access EDEN."
Chinese:
「已強制登出認證用戶」
「現在，無法連結到EDEN」――
Korean:
「인증 유저의 강제 로그아웃이 실행되었습니다」
 현재 EDEN으로의 액세스가 불가능합니다」――

English: It was Erika. She saved us.
Chinese:
是艾莉卡做的……
艾莉卡，救了我們……
German: Das war Erika. Sie hat uns gerettet.

English: What can we do now? This is bad...
German: Was können wir jetzt tun? Das ist übel ...

English:
You heard what she said before we were forced out!
EDEN...
Chinese:
在快被趕出來的時候，我聽到了
艾莉卡的聲音……！
EDEN被――
Korean:
튕겨나가기 직전에 에리카의 목소리가 들렸어…!
EDEN이――
German:
Du hast gehört, was sie sagte, bevor wir
rausgeworfen wurden! EDEN ...

English: EDEN has been eroded by Eaters!
